All right.

367
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:06,200
But I have one condition.

368
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,510
I want to swap seats with you.

369
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,000
Yingzi.

370
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,350
