408
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,790
Not you?

409
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,750
Who does he like?

410
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,720
Anyway, I won't give up so easily.

411
00:19:20,030 --> 00:19:21,270
Who does he like, then?

412
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:31,440
Crimson Saber.

413
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,640
