415
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:51,590
Jiang Yi.

416
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,270
Chloe.

417
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,240
Nice throw.

418
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:06,250
Really?

419
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:06,880
Yeah.

420
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,030
Chloe.

421
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:10,790
Was it really the first game for you both?

422
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:11,240
Yes.

423
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,110
Our first game together.

424
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,590
You two made a perfect team.

425
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:15,270
All right, I'm off.

426
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:15,920
Bye-bye.

427
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,480
Thank you.

428
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,160
Did Ting and Bunnie

429
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,510
invite you for a drink?

430
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:33,830
I turned it down.

431
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:35,590
Why?

432
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,350
I don't want to drink.

433
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:41,000
