434
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,720
Many guys want to hang out with them.

435
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:44,790
Is it?

436
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:46,480
I suppose they don't need me .

437
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:51,200
So you are free now.

438
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:53,720
Will you turn me down

439
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,320
