440
00:20:58,790 --> 00:20:59,680
Why?

441
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,070
You want to invite me for a drink?

442
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:04,880
I would like to take a look at the game you designed before.

443
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,830
Maybe I might come up with some ideas .

444
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:09,680
Sure.

445
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:10,960
I will go home

446
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,960
and fetch the hard disk for you.

447
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,830
I can go to your place.

448
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,030
It is convenient.

449
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:20,680
Well...

450
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:25,270
My house is kind of messy.

451
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,400
I'm not going there for a house tour.

452
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,070
Come on .

453
00:21:32,510 --> 00:21:33,310
Hurry up.

454
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:53,880
