462
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:14,350
That's why I chose ATG.

463
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:18,510
By the look of it,

464
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:19,440
joining Zhao Yuan's team

465
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:21,110
is a waste of your talent.

466
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:24,240
Have you thought about

467
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:25,440
leading your own team?

468
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,830
Zhao Yuan doesn't want me to stay, right?

469
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:34,000
The newcomer Jiang Yi is indeed skillful.

470
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:37,110
However, he seems to have a hard time fitting himself into the teamwork.

471
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:41,400
Don't geniuses like to be alone?

472
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,680
But since he has joined the company,

473
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,350
he should have learned

474
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,350
what teamwork is by now.

475
00:22:50,590 --> 00:22:51,680
All right.

476
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,070
I have reminded him.

477
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:55,200
Are you joining

478
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,350
the gathering next time?

479
00:22:56,350 --> 00:22:57,350
I will also invite him.

480
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,200
I'm not going.

481
00:23:00,510 --> 00:23:01,310
I have to work on the test version

482
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:02,720
as soon as possible.

483
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,510
By the way, Chloe,

484
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:06,680
I have a request .

485
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:07,830
Go on.

486
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,510
After the test version is completed,

487
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:14,440
I hope you can transfer Jiang Yi to another team.

488
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:17,440
I thought they would want you

489
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,590
for your skill.

490
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:20,030
Unexpectedly,

491
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,960
