492
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,830
Do you think

493
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:28,270
I should stay low key?

494
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,310
You said this

495
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:32,350
