496
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,510
Did I?

497
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:35,310
Yeah.

498
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,480
You said it to the fierce director

499
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:37,750
who always chewed people out.

500
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,880
But I think

501
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:45,000
you don't have to do that.

502
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,880
Let your talent shine.

503
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,480
Let him be.

504
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,720
But the one who makes the decision

505
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,070
is me.

506
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:05,750
Thank you.

507
00:24:10,030 --> 00:24:11,030
Do you have any idea?

508
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,160
I will be frank with you.

509
00:24:15,310 --> 00:24:16,960
Your game is delicate.

510
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,310
