518
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,510
into someone's packaging?

519
00:24:39,590 --> 00:24:41,790
Maybe the packaging matches well with you.

520
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:48,960
Forget it.

521
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,830
The boss recommended a novel to me.

522
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,790
He said it was suitable for sandbox games.

523
00:25:00,110 --> 00:25:01,680
I have been thinking about

524
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,240
