531
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:38,830
It truly blows my mind.

532
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:40,640
It has been years

533
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,550
since I read a great story like this.

534
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:43,830
It is a shame

535
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,160
this author hasn't written anything

536
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,310
