537
00:25:48,510 --> 00:25:49,680
I was surprised that you knew him

538
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,030
and had a collection of his books.

539
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,350
(Does it remind you of something?)

540
00:25:58,680 --> 00:25:59,550
(A tenacious life?)

541
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:07,590
