549
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:38,110
You bought a collection of them.

550
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,400
Well...

551
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,720
May I look around here?

552
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:46,110
