576
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,480
Sorry.

577
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:22,270
It is fine.

578
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:27,590
Try to think about it

579
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:28,640
harder.

580
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,720
