583
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,510
We met before.

584
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:37,440
Hello.

585
00:28:38,110 --> 00:28:39,200
Uh... Sorry.

586
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:41,160
